MY SUBJECTS PROPERLY.

277
00:16:15,809 --> 00:16:19,437
THIS PLAGUE, ALL ITS VICTIMS...

278
00:16:21,230 --> 00:16:23,232
IT'S MY FAULT.

279
00:16:24,734 --> 00:16:28,321
MY FAILURE IS
THE REASON YOU'RE HERE.

280
00:16:43,294 --> 00:16:45,171
THE HUMANS COULD NOT STOP US.

281
00:16:45,171 --> 00:16:49,133
I AM YOUR SUPERIOR.
YOU<i> WILL</i> SALUTE.

282
00:16:53,346 --> 00:16:56,265
NOW, REPORT.

283
00:16:56,265 --> 00:16:58,017
<i>ENTERPRISE</i> WAS DESTROYED.

284
00:16:58,017 --> 00:17:00,645
STARFLEET WILL THINK
IT WAS HER ENGINES.

285
00:17:00,645 --> 00:17:03,147
ONE OF YOU IS MISSING.

286
00:17:03,147 --> 00:17:06,150
YOUR SON WAS SLOW.
THE HUMANS KILLED HIM.

287
00:17:08,402 --> 00:17:10,613
DID HE DIE WITH HONOR?

288
00:17:10,613 --> 00:17:14,367
HE LET HUMANS KILL HIM.

289
00:17:30,466 --> 00:17:33,386
[ DOOR OPENS ]

290
00:17:33,386 --> 00:17:34,679
REPORT.

291
00:17:34,679 --> 00:17:37,056
DR. PHLOX HAS MADE
EXCELLENT PROGRESS.

292
00:17:37,056 --> 00:17:38,683
DETAILS.

293
00:17:38,683 --> 00:17:40,518
I'VE IDENTIFIED
THE RNA SEQUENCES THAT CODE --

294
00:17:40,518 --> 00:17:44,271
DETAILS I CAN PASS ON
TO MY SUPERIORS.

295
00:17:44,271 --> 00:17:45,899
I KNOW WHERE TO LOOK

296
00:17:45,899 --> 00:17:48,192
FOR THE SWITCH THAT WILL
TURN OFF THE VIRUS.

297
00:17:48,192 --> 00:17:50,361
HOW LONG UNTIL YOU FIND IT?

298
00:17:50,361 --> 00:17:51,320
AN HOUR.

299
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:53,406
ONE HOUR.

300
00:17:59,119 --> 00:18:00,705
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

301
00:18:00,705 --> 00:18:02,540
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

302
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:04,417
I HAVE NEWS
FOR THE HIGH COUNCIL.

303
00:18:04,417 --> 00:18:06,419
EXPLAIN.

304
00:18:06,419 --> 00:18:09,213
<i>THE DENOBULAN IS CLOSE</i>
<i>TO PERFECTING THE</i>
<i>AUGMENTS' GENOME.</i>

305
00:18:09,213 --> 00:18:11,591
THE COUNCIL HAS
SHUT DOWN YOUR PROJECT.

306
00:18:11,591 --> 00:18:13,509
<i>IF YOU STERILIZE THIS COLONY,</i>

307
00:18:13,509 --> 00:18:16,554
<i>THEN ALL OUR RESEARCH</i>
<i>WILL BE LOST.</i>

308
00:18:19,098 --> 00:18:21,976
<i>THE FLEET WILL REACH YOU</i>
<i>IN THREE DAYS.</i>

309
00:18:21,976 --> 00:18:25,396
<i>IF YOU'RE SUCCESSFUL</i>
<i>BY THE TIME WE GET TO ORBIT,</i>

310
00:18:25,396 --> 00:18:28,190
<i>QU'VAT WILL BE SPARED.</i>

311
00:18:38,785 --> 00:18:40,244
[ DOOR OPENS ]

312
00:18:40,244 --> 00:18:41,955
CAPTAIN,
IT'S GONNA BE A WHILE

313
00:18:41,955 --> 00:18:44,248
BEFORE EVERYTHING'S BACK
TO NORMAL IN ENGINEERING.

314
00:18:44,248 --> 00:18:45,291
CAN KELBY HANDLE IT?

315
00:18:45,291 --> 00:18:47,293
[ SIGHS ]

316
00:18:47,293 --> 00:18:49,587
I COULD PULL A LITTLE DOUBLE
DUTY TO HELP HIM OUT.

317
00:18:49,587 --> 00:18:51,714
I COULD CHECK
WITH CAPTAIN HERNANDEZ.

318
00:18:55,676 --> 00:18:57,386
SOMETHING ELSE?

319
00:18:59,722 --> 00:19:01,641
WHAT THE HELL'S
GOING ON WITH MALCOLM?

320
00:19:03,768 --> 00:19:06,145
NOTHING I CAN GET INTO
RIGHT NOW.

321
00:19:06,145 --> 00:19:08,815
FAIR ENOUGH.

322
00:19:08,815 --> 00:19:11,275
GUESS I'D BETTER
GET BACK TO<i> COLUMBIA.</i>

323
00:19:11,275 --> 00:19:13,402
I'LL WALK WITH YOU.

324
00:19:20,118 --> 00:19:22,161
ARE YOU ENJOYING YOUR TIME
ABOARD<i> COLUMBIA?</i>

325
00:19:22,161 --> 00:19:24,204
SURE, WHY WOULDN'T I?

326
00:19:24,204 --> 00:19:26,624
YOU HAVEN'T BEEN EXPERIENCING
ANY PROBLEMS?

327
00:19:26,624 --> 00:19:28,542
SUCH AS?

328
00:19:28,542 --> 00:19:33,631
ADJUSTING TO NEW FOOD,
NEW ROUTINES...

329
00:19:33,631 --> 00:19:35,133
TROUBLE SLEEPING.

330
00:19:35,133 --> 00:19:38,385
I SLEEP JUST FINE.

331
00:19:38,385 --> 00:19:39,637
HOW ABOUT YOU?

332
00:19:39,637 --> 00:19:41,388
FINE.

333
00:19:41,388 --> 00:19:42,431
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

334
00:19:42,431 --> 00:19:44,017
QUITE.

335
00:19:50,523 --> 00:19:52,859
YOUR HOUR IS UP.

336
00:19:52,859 --> 00:19:54,861
WE ARE GETTING
THE TEST RESULTS NOW.

337
00:19:54,861 --> 00:19:57,697
WE ARE RUNNING OUT OF TIME!

338
00:19:57,697 --> 00:20:01,117
GENERAL, I KNOW THE KLINGON
FLEET IS ON ITS WAY,

339
00:20:01,117 --> 00:20:06,039
AND I UNDERSTAND WHAT THIS
PROJECT COST YOU, PERSONALLY.

340
00:20:06,039 --> 00:20:08,708
ANTAAK TOLD ME ABOUT YOUR SON.

341
00:20:08,708 --> 00:20:11,127
HE DIED IN COMBAT
FOR THE EMPIRE.

342
00:20:11,127 --> 00:20:15,548
AT LEAST HE WAS SPARED THE FINAL
STAGE OF THIS DISEASE.

343
00:20:16,966 --> 00:20:20,845
MAY I, UH, ASK
HOW HE WAS INFECTED?

344
00:20:20,845 --> 00:20:23,723
COMMAND CHOSE HIS UNIT
FOR THE AUGMENT EXPERIMENT

345
00:20:23,723 --> 00:20:26,559
WHEN WE HAD EXHAUSTED
OUR SUPPLY OF PRISONERS.

346
00:20:26,559 --> 00:20:28,811
MY SON WAS A WARRIOR.

347
00:20:28,811 --> 00:20:32,940
HE ASKED FOR NO SPECIAL
TREATMENT, AND I GAVE HIM NONE.

348
00:20:39,739 --> 00:20:42,449
[ TRAY CLATTERS ]

349
00:20:42,449 --> 00:20:44,326
[ SCOFFS ]

350
00:20:44,326 --> 00:20:45,786
WHAT'D THEY GIVE YOU?

351
00:20:45,786 --> 00:20:48,497
IT'S DEAD. I CAN'T EAT THAT.

352
00:20:48,497 --> 00:20:51,417
NO WONDER YOU'RE ALL SO WEAK.

353
00:20:51,417 --> 00:20:53,502
PHYSICAL STRENGTH
ISN'T EVERYTHING.

354
00:20:53,502 --> 00:20:55,504
WELL, YOU CAN'T
WIN WARS WITHOUT IT.

355
00:20:55,504 --> 00:20:58,382
BEING SMART IS MORE IMPORTANT.

356
00:20:58,382 --> 00:21:00,676
GENERAL SUN TZU SAID
THAT THE GREATEST VICTORIES

357
00:21:00,676 --> 00:21:02,511
ARE THOSE WON
WITHOUT FIGHTING.

358
00:21:02,511 --> 00:21:06,599
THE GREAT KAHLESS SAID THERE'S
NO VICTORY WITHOUT COMBAT.

359
00:21:09,227 --> 00:21:12,730
DO YOU EVER QUESTION
WHY YOU FIGHT?

360
00:21:12,730 --> 00:21:16,358
SOLDIERS DON'T QUESTION.
THEY OBEY.

361
00:21:16,358 --> 00:21:20,113
WHAT IF YOUR SUPERIORS
ARE WRONG?

362
00:21:20,113 --> 00:21:24,283
THEY'RE IMPRISONED...OR KILLED.

363
00:21:24,283 --> 00:21:26,702
THAT'S NOT HOW WE DO THINGS
IN STARFLEET.

364
00:21:26,702 --> 00:21:29,914
WHICH IS WHY THE KLINGON EMPIRE
WILL DEFEAT YOU.

365
00:21:31,916 --> 00:21:36,462
THEN HOW COME YOU'RE
IN THE SAME BRIG THAT I'M IN?

366
00:21:40,507 --> 00:21:42,509
YOU SAID WE'D BECOME STRONGER.

367
00:21:42,509 --> 00:21:44,929
THIS IS WHAT
YOU'VE DONE TO US.

368
00:21:44,929 --> 00:21:47,932
HE WILL BECOME INFECTIOUS,
SO HE SHOULD BE QUARANTINED.

369
00:21:47,932 --> 00:21:50,017
WE'LL REMAIN HERE.

370
00:21:50,017 --> 00:21:55,481
IF WE'RE GOING TO DIE, WE'LL DIE
TOGETHER AS COMRADES.

371
00:21:55,481 --> 00:21:57,316
BE PATIENT, LIEUTENANT.

372
00:21:57,316 --> 00:22:00,360
THE DENOBULAN IS WORKING
TO STABILIZE THE HUMAN DNA.

373
00:22:00,360 --> 00:22:04,824
YOU WILL ALL BE HEALTHY AGAIN
AND STRONGER THAN ANY KLINGON.

374
00:22:04,824 --> 00:22:07,576
WILL HE RESTORE
OUR APPEARANCE?

375
00:22:07,576 --> 00:22:09,328
I DON'T KNOW.

376
00:22:09,328 --> 00:22:12,748
HOW DO YOU EXPECT US TO
RETURN HOME LOOKING LIKE THIS?

377
00:22:12,748 --> 00:22:15,126
WE WILL BE OUTCASTS.

378
00:22:15,126 --> 00:22:17,503
THERE WILL BE NO PLACE
FOR US IN THE EMPIRE.

379
00:22:17,503 --> 00:22:20,923
YOUR HEART IS STILL KLINGON.

380
00:22:20,923 --> 00:22:22,967
ARE YOU CERTAIN OF THAT?

381
00:22:24,885 --> 00:22:27,972
DURING THE BATTLE
WITH THE STARFLEET SHIP,

382
00:22:27,972 --> 00:22:32,350
I FELT FEAR FOR THE FIRST TIME
SINCE I WAS A CHILD.

383
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:34,478
I WASN'T ALONE.

384
00:22:34,478 --> 00:22:38,065
I COULD SEE IT IN THE EYES
OF THE OTHERS.

385
00:22:38,065 --> 00:22:40,484
WE'VE BECOME LIKE THEM.

386
00:22:40,484 --> 00:22:42,820
WEAK, COWARDLY.

387
00:22:42,820 --> 00:22:45,614
IT WOULD BE BETTER
FOR US TO DIE.

388
00:22:45,614 --> 00:22:48,159
AS LONG AS I DRAW BREATH,

389
00:22:48,159 --> 00:22:51,662
THE EMPIRE WILL NOT
TURN ITS BACK ON YOU.

390
00:22:58,252 --> 00:23:00,963
I GET THE FEELING
YOU MISS PHLOX, TOO.

391
00:23:03,257 --> 00:23:08,221
MAYBE IT'S JUST THE STASH OF
CHEESE HE'S GOT IN SICK BAY.

392
00:23:08,221 --> 00:23:10,597
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

393
00:23:10,597 --> 00:23:12,558
HOLD THAT THOUGHT.

394
00:23:12,558 --> 00:23:14,518
<i>CAPTAIN ARCHER.</i>

395
00:23:14,518 --> 00:23:17,688
<i>I'M TOLD YOU HAVE</i>
<i>SOME QUESTIONS FOR ME.</i>

396
00:23:17,688 --> 00:23:18,731
WHERE'S MY DOCTOR?

397
00:23:18,731 --> 00:23:20,524
<i>HE'S SAFE,</i>

398
00:23:20,524 --> 00:23:22,735
<i>ON A MISSION OF GREAT</i>
<i>IMPORTANCE TO STARFLEET.</i>

399
00:23:22,735 --> 00:23:24,362
PHLOX WAS KIDNAPPED.

400
00:23:24,362 --> 00:23:26,364
STARFLEET WOULD
NEVER AUTHORIZE THAT.

401
00:23:26,364 --> 00:23:30,408
<i>REREAD THE CHARTER --</i>
<i>ARTICLE 14, SECTION 31.</i>

402
00:23:30,408 --> 00:23:32,578
<i>THERE ARE A FEW LINES</i>
<i>THAT MAKE ALLOWANCES</i>

403
00:23:32,578 --> 00:23:35,706
<i>FOR BENDING THE RULES DURING</i>
<i>TIMES OF EXTRAORDINARY THREAT.</i>

404
00:23:35,706 --> 00:23:37,791
