THAT WHAT WE'RE TALKING ABOUT?

407
00:23:43,923 --> 00:23:47,134
<i>WHAT I WANT TO TALK ABOUT</i>
<i>IS LIEUTENANT REED.</i>

408
00:23:47,134 --> 00:23:49,595
<i>HE'S DONE GOOD WORK</i>
<i>FOR US OVER THE YEARS.</i>

409
00:23:49,595 --> 00:23:51,138
<i>DON'T BE TOO HARD ON HIM.</i>

410
00:23:51,138 --> 00:23:52,848
<i>HE WAS JUST FOLLOWING</i>
<i>MY ORDERS.</i>

411
00:23:52,848 --> 00:23:55,601
YOU PUT HIM
IN AN IMPOSSIBLE POSITION.

412
00:23:55,601 --> 00:23:57,395
<i>I CAN UNDERSTAND WHY YOU</i>
<i>WOULD FEEL THAT WAY,</i>

413
00:23:57,395 --> 00:24:00,189
<i>BUT THIS IS BIGGER</i>
<i>THAN ONE CAPTAIN AND ONE SHIP.</i>

414
00:24:00,189 --> 00:24:02,233
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE
TO DO BETTER THAN THAT.

415
00:24:02,233 --> 00:24:05,236
<i>ALL I CAN TELL YOU IS</i>
<i>THAT IF YOU INTERFERE</i>

416
00:24:05,236 --> 00:24:07,654
<i>BEFORE PHLOX COMPLETES</i>
<i>HIS ASSIGNMENT,</i>

417
00:24:07,654 --> 00:24:10,699
<i>THE REPERCUSSIONS WILL</i>
<i>AFFECT ENTIRE WORLDS.</i>

418
00:24:13,619 --> 00:24:16,663
ONE OF THESE FOUR STRAINS
HAS THE GENETIC TRIGGER

419
00:24:16,663 --> 00:24:18,332
THAT CAN NEUTRALIZE THE VIRUS

420
00:24:18,332 --> 00:24:20,500
BEFORE IT ADVANCES
TO ITS LETHAL STAGE.

421
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:22,753
-WHICH ONE?
-I DON'T KNOW YET.

422
00:24:22,753 --> 00:24:25,423
THAT'S WHY I HAVE
TO CHECK EACH OF THEM.

423
00:24:25,423 --> 00:24:28,926
-HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE?
-A WEEK.

424
00:24:28,926 --> 00:24:31,720
YOUR FLEET CAN QUARANTINE
THIS WORLD, HMM,

425
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:33,389
WHILE I COMPLETE MY TESTS.

426
00:24:33,389 --> 00:24:35,557
STERILIZATION IS NOT NECESSARY.

427
00:24:35,557 --> 00:24:38,685
FLEET ADMIRAL KRELL
WILL NOT EXTEND HIS DEADLINE.

428
00:24:38,685 --> 00:24:41,563
THE ONLY POSSIBLE WAY TO GET
RESULTS ON KRELL'S SCHEDULE

429
00:24:41,563 --> 00:24:43,816
IS TO INFECT
FOUR HEALTHY KLINGONS.

430
00:24:43,816 --> 00:24:45,692
YOU HAVE FOUR RIGHT HERE!

431
00:24:45,692 --> 00:24:48,695
ONLY ONE OF THESE STRAINS
WILL WORK.

432
00:24:48,695 --> 00:24:50,239
THE OTHER THREE WILL BE LETHAL.

433
00:24:50,239 --> 00:24:52,074
ETHICALLY, IT'S UNTHINKABLE!

434
00:24:52,074 --> 00:24:55,161
THE ETHICS, DOCTOR, ARE SIMPLE.

435
00:24:55,161 --> 00:24:58,580
THREE LIVES TO SAVE MILLIONS.

436
00:25:03,169 --> 00:25:06,630
