IT DIDN'T SEEM LIKE LYING.

437
00:25:06,630 --> 00:25:07,840
WHAT ELSE WOULD YOU CALL IT?

438
00:25:07,840 --> 00:25:09,549
COVERT OPERATIONS.

439
00:25:09,549 --> 00:25:13,304
I WAS A YOUNG ENSIGN.
IT WAS...EXCITING.

440
00:25:13,304 --> 00:25:15,639
HOW DO YOU FEEL ABOUT IT NOW?

441
00:25:15,639 --> 00:25:18,558
I THOUGHT IT WAS DONE.

442
00:25:18,558 --> 00:25:22,229
THIS IS THE FIRST TIME
THAT HARRIS HAS CONTACTED ME

443
00:25:22,229 --> 00:25:24,731
SINCE I'VE SERVED ON<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

444
00:25:24,731 --> 00:25:26,524
HE TOLD ME ABOUT THE PLAGUE.

445
00:25:26,524 --> 00:25:29,527
HE SAID THEY NEEDED PHLOX TO
HELP THE KLINGONS FIND A CURE.

446
00:25:29,527 --> 00:25:32,031
I WAS SUPPOSED
TO JUST SLOW US DOWN.

447
00:25:32,031 --> 00:25:35,159
DID HARRIS TELL YOU ABOUT THIS?

448
00:25:37,411 --> 00:25:39,705
I HAD T'POL TAKE A CLOSER LOOK
AT OUR PRISONER'S MEDICAL SCANS.

449
00:25:39,705 --> 00:25:42,958
IT'S HUMAN DNA.

450
00:25:42,958 --> 00:25:46,128
I'M GUESSING THE PLAGUE
IS A SIDE EFFECT

451
00:25:46,128 --> 00:25:48,714
OF A MILITARY EXPERIMENT
THAT WENT WRONG.

452
00:25:48,714 --> 00:25:50,049
