HARRIS CLAIMS HE'S DOING THIS

454
00:25:51,884 --> 00:25:55,929
BECAUSE STARFLEET NEEDS
A STABLE KLINGON EMPIRE.

455
00:25:58,474 --> 00:26:00,642
DO YOU BELIEVE HIM?

456
00:26:00,642 --> 00:26:04,480
I DON'T TRUST HIM.

457
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:07,441
IF THE KLINGONS NEEDED OUR HELP,
THERE ARE EASIER WAYS TO GET IT.

458
00:26:09,151 --> 00:26:11,862
I WANTED TO TELL YOU EVERYTHING,
CAPTAIN.

459
00:26:15,741 --> 00:26:18,618
THERE'S A WAY OUT OF THIS.

460
00:26:18,618 --> 00:26:20,578
I DON'T HAVE TO PUT YOU
BACK IN THE BRIG,

461
00:26:20,578 --> 00:26:23,332
BUT YOU HAVE TO CHOOSE
WHERE YOUR LOYALTIES LIE.

462
00:26:25,709 --> 00:26:27,794
I WASN'T TOLD
WHERE PHLOX WAS TAKEN,

463
00:26:27,794 --> 00:26:30,588
BUT STARFLEET INTELLIGENCE
BELIEVES THE KLINGONS HAVE

464
00:26:30,588 --> 00:26:35,677
A GENETIC RESEARCH FACILITY
ON QU'VAT COLONY.

465
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,531
AS YOU WERE.

466
00:27:02,746 --> 00:27:04,998
HOW LONG UNTIL
WE REACH QU'VAT?

467
00:27:04,998 --> 00:27:06,833
SIX HOURS, SIR.

468
00:27:06,833 --> 00:27:09,795
CAPTAIN, WE NEED TO BE READY
FOR KLINGON PATROLS.

469
00:27:09,795 --> 00:27:12,465
I SUGGEST THAT<i> COLUMBIA</i>
WITHDRAWS TO A SAFER DISTANCE,

470
00:27:12,465 --> 00:27:14,174
SO THAT WE DON'T
MAKE A SINGLE TARGET.

471
00:27:14,174 --> 00:27:17,052
OPEN A CHANNEL
TO CAPTAIN HERNANDEZ.

472
00:27:18,762 --> 00:27:23,016
WHY DID YOU THINK YOU'D
SUCCEED IN PERFECTING AUGMENTS

473
00:27:23,016 --> 00:27:24,477
WHEN DR. SOONG FAILED?

474
00:27:24,477 --> 00:27:27,605
SOONG'S MISTAKE WAS THAT
HE MADE TOO FEW OF THEM.

475
00:27:27,605 --> 00:27:31,233
EARTH ONCE HAD THOUSANDS.
THEY BECAME TYRANNICAL
AND STARTED A WAR.

476
00:27:31,233 --> 00:27:34,194
-KLINGONS HAVE DISCIPLINE.
-AUGMENTS DON'T.

477
00:27:34,194 --> 00:27:35,988
THEIR INCREASED AGGRESSION

478
00:27:35,988 --> 00:27:38,115
IS MATCHED BY THEIR
DECREASED INHIBITIONS.

479
00:27:38,115 --> 00:27:41,494
YOU'D LOSE CONTROL OF THEM,
JUST AS HUMANS DID.

480
00:27:53,713 --> 00:27:56,674
HOW LONG UNTIL WE KNOW
WHICH ONE OF US SURVIVES?

481
00:27:56,674 --> 00:27:59,011
AN HOUR, AT MOST.

482
00:28:00,262 --> 00:28:02,556
WOULD BLOODWINE
AFFECT THE RESULTS?

483
00:28:02,556 --> 00:28:04,933
I DON'T BELIEVE SO.

484
00:28:04,933 --> 00:28:07,978
THEN WE SHALL DRINK...
[ LAUGHS ]

485
00:28:07,978 --> 00:28:10,856
...TO THE BRAVERY
OF THESE WARRIORS.

486
00:28:10,856 --> 00:28:11,940
DOCTOR!

487
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:14,818
NEVER ON THE JOB.

488
00:28:14,818 --> 00:28:16,694
[ CHUCKLES ]

489
00:28:16,694 --> 00:28:19,615
WE KNOW PHLOX WAS TAKEN TO
QU'VAT COLONY TO WORK ON A CURE.

490
00:28:19,615 --> 00:28:21,992
WE'RE GONNA BE THERE
IN LESS THAN AN HOUR.

491
00:28:21,992 --> 00:28:23,160
[ COUGHING ]

492
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:25,496
KRELL'S PATROLS
WILL CRUSH YOU.

493
00:28:25,496 --> 00:28:29,416
THEY'VE ALL BEEN RECALLED
TO ENFORCE QUARANTINE ZONES.

494
00:28:29,416 --> 00:28:31,751
PHLOX WILL BE IN
THE MEDICAL FACILITY.

495
00:28:31,751 --> 00:28:33,504
WE NEED THE COORDINATES.

496
00:28:33,504 --> 00:28:36,131
[ COUGHS ]

497
00:28:37,757 --> 00:28:41,387
IF YOU DON'T WANT TO HELP US,
HELP YOUR PEOPLE.

498
00:28:55,067 --> 00:28:58,153
MY BROTHERS.

499
00:28:58,153 --> 00:29:02,032
THEY'RE QUITE ILL.
SO ARE YOU.

500
00:29:02,032 --> 00:29:04,076
TRY TO REST.

501
00:29:04,076 --> 00:29:05,952
DOCTOR.

502
00:29:05,952 --> 00:29:09,122
THE TWO GUARDS ARE DISPLAYING
THE FIRST SYMPTOMS.

503
00:29:10,957 --> 00:29:14,211
THAT ACCOUNTS FOR TWO
OF THE THREE LETHAL STRAINS.

504
00:29:14,211 --> 00:29:17,673
SO EITHER GENERAL K'VAGH LIVES,
OR I DO.

505
00:29:19,550 --> 00:29:21,176
[ SCANNER BEEPS ]

506
00:29:28,850 --> 00:29:32,771
IT'S THE GENERAL, ISN'T IT?
HIS STRAIN HAS THE CURE.

507
00:29:32,771 --> 00:29:35,566
IF WE WORK QUICKLY, THERE'S A
CHANCE WE CAN TREAT YOU IN TIME.

508
00:29:45,284 --> 00:29:47,411
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

509
00:29:47,411 --> 00:29:48,621
WHAT NOW?

510
00:29:48,621 --> 00:29:50,706
<i>THERE'S BEEN A COMPLICATION.</i>

511
00:29:50,706 --> 00:29:52,958
ANOTHER ONE?

512
00:29:52,958 --> 00:29:55,335
<i>THIS TIME,</i> YOUR<i> PEOPLE</i>
<i>FAILED TO STOP</i> ENTERPRISE.

513
00:29:55,335 --> 00:29:57,504
<i>IT'S ON ITS WAY TO QU'VAT,</i>
<i>WITH</i> COLUMBIA.

514
00:29:57,504 --> 00:29:59,632
ORDER THEM TO WITHDRAW.

515
00:29:59,632 --> 00:30:01,216
<i>YOU KNOW I DON'T HAVE</i>
<i>THAT AUTHORITY.</i>

516
00:30:01,216 --> 00:30:03,469
THEN I'LL DESTROY THEM.

517
00:30:03,469 --> 00:30:07,013
<i>WE HAD AN ARRANGEMENT.</i>

518
00:30:07,013 --> 00:30:09,725
YOU DID WHAT I WANTED.

519
00:30:09,725 --> 00:30:11,851
I DON'T NEED YOU ANYMORE.

520
00:30:11,851 --> 00:30:14,229
<i>YOU AGREED THAT BOTH</i>
<i>OUR GOVERNMENTS WOULD BENEFIT</i>

521
00:30:14,229 --> 00:30:15,939
<i>IF THE TWO OF US</i>
<i>WORKED TOGETHER.</i>

522
00:30:15,939 --> 00:30:20,235
AND YOU BELIEVED ME.

523
00:30:20,235 --> 00:30:21,654
LOAD THE AMINO ACIDS.

524
00:30:21,654 --> 00:30:24,448
I'LL EXTRACT THE VIRAL DNA
FROM HIS BLOOD.

525
00:30:29,869 --> 00:30:30,912
CAPTAIN.

526
00:30:30,912 --> 00:30:32,122
YOU ALL RIGHT?

527
00:30:32,122 --> 00:30:34,124
BETTER, NOW THAT YOU'RE HERE.

528
00:30:34,124 --> 00:30:35,834
FATHER.

529
00:30:37,336 --> 00:30:40,088
I WAS TOLD
THAT YOU HAD BEEN KILLED.

530
00:30:40,088 --> 00:30:42,966
THE HUMANS SPARED ME.

531
00:30:42,966 --> 00:30:45,719
-I CAME TO GET MY DOCTOR BACK.
-WE NEED HIM HERE.

532
00:30:45,719 --> 00:30:47,971
I HAVE TWO SHIPS IN ORBIT,
HEAVILY ARMED.

533
00:30:47,971 --> 00:30:50,766
GENTLEMEN, PLEASE.
I THINK I CAN SPEAK FOR MYSELF.

534
00:30:50,766 --> 00:30:52,476
CAPTAIN.

535
00:30:52,476 --> 00:30:54,603
I NEED A LITTLE MORE TIME
TO CURE THIS PLAGUE.

536
00:30:54,603 --> 00:30:56,355
CURE?

537
00:30:56,355 --> 00:30:59,191
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO PERFECT
THE AUGMENT GENOME!

538
00:30:59,191 --> 00:31:01,819
I LIED.
YOUR SON MAY BE ALIVE,

539
00:31:01,819 --> 00:31:03,445
BUT HE WILL NOT SURVIVE
MUCH LONGER

540
00:31:03,445 --> 00:31:05,698
UNLESS I COMPLETE MY WORK.

541
00:31:05,698 --> 00:31:08,908
A FEW HOURS, CAPTAIN --
THAT'S ALL I ASK.

542
00:31:08,908 --> 00:31:11,370
SEVERAL MILLION PATIENTS
ARE COUNTING ON IT.

543
00:31:11,370 --> 00:31:13,872
-[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]
-COMMANDER.

544
00:31:13,872 --> 00:31:16,709
THREE KLINGON BATTLE CRUISERS
HAVE JUST DROPPED OUT OF WARP.

545
00:31:16,709 --> 00:31:19,252
OPEN A CHANNEL TO<i> COLUMBIA.</i>

546
00:31:19,252 --> 00:31:20,838
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

547
00:31:20,838 --> 00:31:22,840
THE KLINGONS ARE
JAMMING EVERYTHING.

548
00:31:22,840 --> 00:31:24,883
[ ALARM BLARING ]

549
00:31:24,883 --> 00:31:26,426
WHAT IS IT?

550
00:31:26,426 --> 00:31:29,471
-KRELL'S SHIPS ARE HERE.
-KEEP WORKING.

551
00:31:29,471 --> 00:31:32,140
-[ COMMUNICATOR BEEPS ]
-ARCHER TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

552
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:34,518
TELL THE KLINGONS
WE HAVE THE CURE.

553
00:31:36,645 --> 00:31:38,438
<i>ENTERPRISE,</i> RESPOND.

554
00:31:38,438 --> 00:31:40,691
This is Fleet Admiral Krell.

555
00:31:40,691 --> 00:31:43,902
I'M UNDER ORDERS TO
ERADICATE THIS COLONY.

556
00:31:43,902 --> 00:31:48,156
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THAT.
MY DOCTOR CAN STOP THE PLAGUE.

557
00:31:48,156 --> 00:31:52,369
I HAVE
A MORE EFFECTIVE SOLUTION.

558
00:31:52,369 --> 00:31:56,081
HELLO, ADMIRAL KRELL.
THIS IS DR. PHLOX.

559
00:31:56,081 --> 00:32:00,001
I AM TRANSMITTING
THE DETAILS OF AN ANTIVIRUS.

560
00:32:00,001 --> 00:32:02,755
FEEL FREE TO HAVE YOUR
PHYSICIANS CONFIRM MY FINDINGS,

561
00:32:02,755 --> 00:32:06,383
AND YOU'RE WELCOME TO CALL
WITH ANY QUESTIONS.

562
00:32:06,383 --> 00:32:08,301
My orders are clear.

563
00:32:08,301 --> 00:32:10,095
CAPTAIN ARCHER,

564
00:32:10,095 --> 00:32:14,140
YOUR SHIPS ARE NOW THE PROPERTY
OF THE KLINGON EMPIRE.

565
00:32:14,140 --> 00:32:17,060
STAND DOWN OR BE DESTROYED.

566
00:32:26,069 --> 00:32:28,154
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

567
00:32:28,154 --> 00:32:31,366
PROCEED AS PLANNED.

568
00:32:31,366 --> 00:32:34,244
LEAVE NOTHING STANDING.

569
00:32:34,244 --> 00:32:36,872
THE LEAD SHIP'S MOVING
INTO A LOWER ORBIT.

570
00:32:36,872 --> 00:32:38,164
THEY'RE CHARGING WEAPONS.

571
00:32:38,164 --> 00:32:40,041
INTERCEPT COURSE.

572
00:32:40,041 --> 00:32:42,961
<i>-COLUMBIA.</i> 
-[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

573
00:32:42,961 --> 00:32:44,129
I CAN'T GET THROUGH.

574
00:32:44,129 --> 00:32:45,547
THEY'RE FIRING ON THE COLONY.

575
00:32:45,547 --> 00:32:47,090
TARGET THEIR DISRUPTORS.

576
00:32:57,517 --> 00:33:00,103
HOW STRONG ARE THE SHIELDS
AROUND THIS PLACE?

577
00:33:00,103 --> 00:33:02,648
NOT STRONG ENOUGH!

578
00:33:02,648 --> 00:33:04,483
YOU SAID YOU HAD
TWO SHIPS IN ORBIT.

579
00:33:04,483 --> 00:33:06,777
I'M SURE THEY'RE DOING
EVERYTHING THEY CAN.

580
00:33:06,777 --> 00:33:08,403
-[ COMMUNICATOR BEEPS ]
-ARCHER TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

581
00:33:08,403 --> 00:33:10,113
[ Static ]

582
00:33:19,164 --> 00:33:22,334
THEY'RE CLOSING FROM ASTERN.

583
00:33:22,334 --> 00:33:24,210
AFT CANNONS ARE DOWN.

584
00:33:30,300 --> 00:33:32,469
<i>COLUMBIA</i> TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

585
00:33:32,469 --> 00:33:34,346
LOOKED LIKE YOU
COULD USE A HAND.

586
00:33:34,346 --> 00:33:35,889
[ Static ]

587
00:33:35,889 --> 00:33:39,142
LET'S KEEP THOSE SHIPS
OFF THEIR TAIL.

588
00:33:40,393 --> 00:33:43,146
YOUR SHIPS ARE TAKING DAMAGE.

589
00:33:43,146 --> 00:33:45,357
HOW MUCH LONGER?

590
00:33:45,357 --> 00:33:47,108
AS I SAID, ANOTHER FEW HOURS.

591
00:33:47,108 --> 00:33:49,444
CAN YOU SPEED THAT UP
A LITTLE?

592
00:33:49,444 --> 00:33:51,070
PHLOX, I'VE GOT AN IDEA.

593
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:52,990
BUT IF WE WANT TO GET OUT
OF HERE IN ONE PIECE,

594
00:33:52,990 --> 00:33:55,450
WE'VE GOT TO GET THAT CURE,
AND WE'VE GOT TO GET IT FAST.

595
00:33:59,579 --> 00:34:01,832
I COULD FINISH THE ANTIVIRUS
IN LESS TIME

596
00:34:01,832 --> 00:34:05,335
IF I HAD A HUMAN HOST TO
REPLICATE ENOUGH ANTIBODIES.

597
00:34:07,546 --> 00:34:09,673
I DON'T SEE
ANY OTHER HUMANS AROUND.

598
00:34:09,673 --> 00:34:11,591
CAPTAIN, I WOULD HAVE
TO EXPOSE YOU TO THE PLAGUE.

599
00:34:11,591 --> 00:34:12,885
I CANNOT PREDICT
WHAT IT MIGHT DO TO YOU.

600
00:34:12,885 --> 00:34:16,054
-WILL IT GIVE YOU THE CURE?
-UNQUESTIONABLY.

601
00:34:16,054 --> 00:34:17,472
LET'S GET STARTED.

602
00:34:19,307 --> 00:34:20,976
WHAT DO YOU INTEND TO DO?

603
00:34:20,976 --> 00:34:24,229
THIS VIRUS MAY BE OUR
BEST WEAPON AGAINST KRELL.

604
00:34:26,147 --> 00:34:27,315
READY WHEN YOU ARE.

605
00:34:33,321 --> 00:34:35,114
ONE OF THE SHIPS
IS LOSING POWER.

606
00:34:35,114 --> 00:34:37,325
THEIR PORT NACELLE
IS VULNERABLE.

607
00:34:37,325 --> 00:34:39,494
THEN FIRE AT WILL.

608
00:34:46,251 --> 00:34:48,127
IN ADDITION TO THE VIRUS,

609
00:34:48,127 --> 00:34:50,380
I'M INJECTING YOU
WITH A METABOLIC CATALYST

610
00:34:50,380 --> 00:34:52,382
TO ACCELERATE
YOUR IMMUNE RESPONSE.

611
00:34:52,382 --> 00:34:53,967
IT WON'T BE PLEASANT.

612
00:35:04,811 --> 00:35:07,439
IT'S NO USE. I CAN'T PENETRATE
THEIR SHIELDS.

613
00:35:07,439 --> 00:35:10,567
COMMANDER, I'VE BROKEN THROUGH
THEIR JAMMING FREQUENCIES.

614
00:35:10,567 --> 00:35:14,446
-[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]
-T'POL TO CAPTAIN ARCHER.

615
00:35:16,155 --> 00:35:18,075
-[ Static ]
-Captain, respond!

616
00:35:18,075 --> 00:35:20,035
-[ GRUNTING ]
-DR. PHLOX HERE.

617
00:35:20,035 --> 00:35:22,454
THE CAPTAIN IS
INDISPOSED AT THE MOMENT.

618
00:35:22,454 --> 00:35:24,539
I imagine you have
your hands full up there.

619
00:35:24,539 --> 00:35:26,124
TO SAY THE LEAST.

620
00:35:26,124 --> 00:35:27,793
WE HAVE A PLAN
TO DEFUSE THE SITUATION,

621
00:35:27,793 --> 00:35:30,420
BUT WE'LL NEED A FEW MORE
MINUTES TO CARRY IT OUT.

622
00:35:31,797 --> 00:35:33,465
I'D APPRECIATE IT IF YOU
COULD KEEP THE CEILING

623
00:35:33,465 --> 00:35:35,383
FROM CAVING IN ON US
UNTIL THEN.

624
00:35:35,383 --> 00:35:36,718
Understood.

625
00:35:38,177 --> 00:35:40,221
HOW MUCH HULL PLATING
DO WE HAVE LEFT?

626
00:35:40,221 --> 00:35:41,514
62%.

627
00:35:41,514 --> 00:35:43,725
MR. MAYWEATHER,
PUT US DIRECTLY

628
00:35:43,725 --> 00:35:45,602
BETWEEN THAT CRUISER
AND THE COLONY.

629
00:35:45,602 --> 00:35:47,562
YOU MAY WANT TO DIVERT
ALL AVAILABLE POWER

630
00:35:47,562 --> 00:35:49,064
TO OUR DORSAL PLATING.

631
00:35:49,064 --> 00:35:51,149
AYE, AYE.

632
00:35:51,149 --> 00:35:52,567
[ GRUNTING ]

633
00:35:59,116 --> 00:36:00,659
IT'S WORKING.

634
00:36:19,678 --> 00:36:22,514
-THEY'RE SHIFTING THEIR ORBIT.
-STAY WITH THEM.

635
00:36:22,514 --> 00:36:25,058
-HULL PLATING'S DOWN TO 40%.
-KEEP FIRING.

636
00:36:26,768 --> 00:36:28,645
CAPTAIN HERNANDEZ,
PLEASE DIRECT YOUR WEAPONS

637
00:36:28,645 --> 00:36:30,355
AT THE BATTLE CRUISER.

638
00:36:30,355 --> 00:36:32,732
WISH I COULD HELP.
WE JUST LOST OUR WEAPONS.

639
00:36:43,160 --> 00:36:45,078
IT'S DONE. HOLD HIM.

640
00:36:48,165 --> 00:36:51,209
AAH!

641
00:36:53,252 --> 00:36:55,254
WE'VE GOT IT!

642
00:36:55,254 --> 00:36:57,549
IS THE CANISTER READY?

643
00:36:57,549 --> 00:37:00,426
IT'S SET TO DISPERSE
FIVE SECONDS AFTER TRANSPORT.

644
00:37:00,426 --> 00:37:01,678
SEND IT.

645
00:37:01,678 --> 00:37:04,556
OPEN A CHANNEL TO KRELL.

646
00:37:12,147 --> 00:37:13,940
HULL PLATING'S NEARLY DOWN.

647
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:16,026
WE CAN'T HOLD THIS POSITION
MUCH LONGER.

648
00:37:17,402 --> 00:37:21,322
ADMIRAL KRELL,
DR. PHLOX AGAIN.

649
00:37:21,322 --> 00:37:22,991
BY NOW YOU MAY HAVE NOTICED

650
00:37:22,991 --> 00:37:25,660
the small package
which we sent to your bridge.

651
00:37:25,660 --> 00:37:27,954
What you may not know
is that it contains

652
00:37:27,954 --> 00:37:30,331
a potent sample of
the metagenic virus.

653
00:37:30,331 --> 00:37:31,583
Even as we speak,

654
00:37:31,583 --> 00:37:33,501
it is dispersing
throughout your ship,

655
00:37:33,501 --> 00:37:35,378
infecting you and your crew.

656
00:37:35,378 --> 00:37:38,173
YOU'RE LYING!

657
00:37:38,173 --> 00:37:40,675
Check your internal sensors.
You will find

658
00:37:40,675 --> 00:37:42,427
THAT THE ATMOSPHERE CONTAINS

659
00:37:42,427 --> 00:37:44,971
APPROXIMATELY 20 PARTS PER
MILLION OF THE VIRAL STRAIN.

660
00:37:44,971 --> 00:37:48,266
OR IF YOU DON'T TRUST YOUR
SENSORS, TRUST YOUR SENSES.

661
00:37:48,266 --> 00:37:52,229
YOU WILL FEEL
THE INITIAL SYMPTOMS
IN ABOUT 30 MINUTES --

662
00:37:52,229 --> 00:37:55,107
A TIGHTNESS IN THE CHEST,
IRREGULAR HEARTBEAT,

663
00:37:55,107 --> 00:37:57,192
TINGLING IN
YOUR CRANIAL RIDGES.

664
00:37:57,192 --> 00:38:00,112
THIS IS A COWARDLY ATTACK!

665
00:38:00,112 --> 00:38:03,322
MAYBE SO. BUT I AM PREPARED
TO GIVE YOU THE CURE.

666
00:38:03,322 --> 00:38:05,324
THANKS TO CAPTAIN ARCHER,

667
00:38:05,324 --> 00:38:07,202
I HAVE MANAGED
TO COMPLETE THE ANTIVIRUS.

668
00:38:07,202 --> 00:38:10,163
OF COURSE, IF YOU
DESTROY THIS COLONY, WELL,

669
00:38:10,163 --> 00:38:13,959
TREATING YOU AND YOUR CREW
COULD PROVE DIFFICULT.

670
00:38:13,959 --> 00:38:17,378
I SUGGEST YOU POWER DOWN
YOUR WEAPONS, ADMIRAL,

671
00:38:17,378 --> 00:38:20,090
AND LET ME CURE YOUR PEOPLE.

672
00:38:21,299 --> 00:38:23,593
[ SIGHS ]

673
00:38:25,929 --> 00:38:28,431
CAPTAIN'S STARLOG,
SUPPLEMENTAL.

674
00:38:28,431 --> 00:38:31,017
ADMIRAL KRELL HAS
CONVINCED THE HIGH COUNCIL

675
00:38:31,017 --> 00:38:33,561
TO CALL OFF
THEIR STERILIZATION PROGRAM.

676
00:38:33,561 --> 00:38:38,066
THEY'VE PROMISED TO
DISTRIBUTE PHLOX'S CURE
THROUGHOUT THE EMPIRE.

677
00:38:38,066 --> 00:38:41,945
THERE'S NO TRACE OF THE VIRUS
IN YOUR BLOODSTREAM.

678
00:38:41,945 --> 00:38:46,449
MY TARG WON'T EVEN
RECOGNIZE ME.

679
00:38:46,449 --> 00:38:48,034
IN THE FUTURE,

680
00:38:48,034 --> 00:38:50,829
IT MAY BE POSSIBLE TO REVERSE
THE COSMETIC EFFECTS.

681
00:38:50,829 --> 00:38:54,457
I SUPPOSE
THIS IS WHAT I DESERVE.

682
00:38:54,457 --> 00:38:59,712
MILLIONS OF MY PEOPLE WILL HAVE
TO LIVE WITH THIS DISFIGUREMENT.

683
00:38:59,712 --> 00:39:03,008
IT'LL BE PASSED
ON TO OUR CHILDREN.

684
00:39:03,008 --> 00:39:04,676
LIFE WON'T BE EASY FOR US.

685
00:39:04,676 --> 00:39:06,928
YOU DID YOUR BEST TO
CORRECT YOUR MISTAKES.

686
00:39:06,928 --> 00:39:09,014
THAT'S ALL WE CAN
ASK OF OURSELVES.

687
00:39:09,014 --> 00:39:13,601
I DOUBT MY SUPERIORS WILL ALLOW
ME TO REMAIN IN MY POSITION.

688
00:39:13,601 --> 00:39:15,937
I'LL NEED TO FIND
A NEW SPECIALTY.

689
00:39:18,564 --> 00:39:21,442
PERHAPS CRANIAL
RECONSTRUCTION.

690
00:39:21,442 --> 00:39:25,780
I HAVE A FEELING THAT'S
ABOUT TO BECOME VERY POPULAR.

691
00:39:33,412 --> 00:39:38,001
I'M GRATEFUL FOR EVERYTHING
THAT YOU'VE DONE.

692
00:39:42,297 --> 00:39:44,549
-[ SIGHS ]
-HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

693
00:39:44,549 --> 00:39:48,427
NOT TOO BAD, ASIDE FROM SOME
STRANGE CRAVINGS.

694
00:39:48,427 --> 00:39:51,181
A PLATEFUL OF LIVE GAGH
SOUNDS PRETTY GOOD RIGHT NOW.

695
00:39:51,181 --> 00:39:54,684
THE CRAVINGS SHOULD DISAPPEAR
IN A DAY OR SO,

696
00:39:54,684 --> 00:39:56,102
ALONG WITH YOUR, UH, RIDGES.

697
00:39:56,102 --> 00:39:59,314
NO, I'D KEEP THEM
IF I WERE YOU, CAPTAIN.

698
00:39:59,314 --> 00:40:01,607
IT MAKES YOU LOOK INTIMIDATING.

699
00:40:01,607 --> 00:40:04,402
I SHOULD GET BACK ON THE ROAD.

700
00:40:04,402 --> 00:40:07,780
ONE OF US NEEDS TO GET
SOME EXPLORING DONE.

701
00:40:07,780 --> 00:40:09,532
THANKS FOR YOUR HELP.

702
00:40:09,532 --> 00:40:13,119
I DON'T KNOW HOW YOU SURVIVED
ALL THESE YEARS WITHOUT ME.

703
00:40:15,997 --> 00:40:17,874
SHOULDN'T YOU BE JOINING HER?

704
00:40:17,874 --> 00:40:19,625
I ASKED TRIP TO STICK
AROUND FOR A LITTLE WHILE

705
00:40:19,625 --> 00:40:21,169
TO HELP US OUT WITH REPAIRS.

706
00:40:21,169 --> 00:40:23,171
INDEED.

707
00:40:23,171 --> 00:40:25,757
OUR NEW CHIEF ENGINEER WILL NO
DOUBT BE DELIGHTED FOR THE HELP.

708
00:40:25,757 --> 00:40:27,842
NO, KELBY'S GOT
NOTHING TO WORRY ABOUT.

709
00:40:27,842 --> 00:40:29,510
I'M ONLY HERE TEMPORARILY.

710
00:40:37,394 --> 00:40:38,811
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

711
00:40:46,444 --> 00:40:47,987
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

712
00:40:47,987 --> 00:40:49,530
<i>I CALLED TO THANK YOU.</i>

713
00:40:49,530 --> 00:40:51,866
<i>EVERYTHING WENT</i>
<i>ACCORDING TO OUR PROJECTIONS.</i>

714
00:40:51,866 --> 00:40:55,494
<i>THE EMPIRE'S BEEN STABILIZED.</i>
<i>I DOUBT VERY MUCH</i>

715
00:40:55,494 --> 00:40:57,872
<i>THEY'LL BE EXPERIMENTING</i>
<i>WITH AUGMENTS ANY TIME SOON.</i>

716
00:40:57,872 --> 00:41:00,625
WE COULD'VE EXPLAINED
EVERYTHING TO CAPTAIN ARCHER.

717
00:41:00,625 --> 00:41:02,585
<i>THAT'S NOT HOW KRELL</i>
<i>WANTED THINGS DONE.</i>

718
00:41:02,585 --> 00:41:05,755
SINCE WHEN DO WE DO THINGS
THE WAY THE KLINGONS WANT?

719
00:41:05,755 --> 00:41:08,216
<i>WHEN IT'S IN OUR INTEREST.</i>

720
00:41:08,216 --> 00:41:10,385
<i>I HAD TO KEEP CERTAIN DETAILS</i>
<i>FROM YOU AS WELL.</i>

721
00:41:10,385 --> 00:41:13,054
<i>I HOPE THERE ARE</i>
<i>NO HARD FEELINGS.</i>

722
00:41:13,054 --> 00:41:15,807
<i>THIS MISSION</i>
<i>WOULDN'T HAVE SUCCEEDED</i>
<i>WITHOUT YOU, LIEUTENANT.</i>

723
00:41:15,807 --> 00:41:19,894
DON'T EVER CONTACT ME AGAIN.
IS THAT CLEAR?

724
00:41:19,894 --> 00:41:23,773
<i>MAYBE YOU DIDN'T UNDERSTAND</i>
<i>OUR RECRUITMENT POLICY.</i>

725
00:41:23,773 --> 00:41:25,775
<i>YOU CAN'T SIMPLY WALK AWAY.</i>

726
00:41:25,775 --> 00:41:29,904
I ANSWER TO ONE COMMANDING
OFFICER -- JONATHAN ARCHER.

727
00:41:29,904 --> 00:41:32,157
<i>LIEUTENANT, WHY DON'T WE --</i>
